        <item>
          <title>CES 2025: Hisense L9Q Laser TV Unveiled with 100-150 Inch 4K Projection and Dolby Atmos Speakers</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Hisense has unveiled its new laser TV, the L9Q, at CES 2025. The TV features a 4K projector that can deliver up to 150 inches of picture size, a new-gen light-rejecting projector screen in five sizes, and Dolby Atmos/DTS:X support with 6.2.2 built-in speaker channels.]]></description>
